<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title><%= nickname %>님의 정원</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    body {
      background: #F4F4F4;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .main-wrapper {
      position: relative;
      width: 402px;
      height: 874px;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header-text {
      position: absolute;
      top: 45px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 30px;
      color: #000;
    }
    .level-text {
      position: absolute;
      top: 88px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #000;
    }
    .button-group {
      position: absolute;
      top: 125px;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 15px;
    }
    .button-group button {
      width: 131px;
      height: 46px;
      background: #FFFFFF;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 2px solid #000;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 18px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .mission-status-box {
      position: absolute;
      top: 648px;
      left: 42px;
      width: 318px;
      height: 109px;
      background: #FFFFFF;
      border: 1px solid #000000;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .mission-status-box .status-text {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .mission-button {
      width: 298px;
      height: 42px;
      background: #F5B600;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 20px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }


  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="main-wrapper" style="background-image: url('/images/tree/<%= fruitName %>_<%= missionCompleted %>.png');">
    <div class="header-text"><%= nickname %>님의 정원</div>
    <div class="level-text"><%= level %>단계</div>

    <div class="button-group">
      <button onclick="location.href='/collection?category=basic&page=1'">📖 도감</button>
      <button onclick="location.href='/inventory'">👜 인벤토리</button>
    </div>

    <div class="mission-status-box">
      <div class="status-text">미션 <%= missionTotal %> / 5 완료</div>
      <button class="mission-button" onclick="location.href='/dashboard/mission'">오늘의 미션 하러 가기</button>
    </div>

    <div class="bottom-nav">
      <div onclick="location.href='/market'">🛖 그로우마켓</div>
      <div onclick="location.href='/home'">🏡 홈</div>
      <div onclick="location.href='/community'">👥 커뮤니티</div>
      <div onclick="location.href='/mypage'">👤 마이페이지</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
